WEBVTT

00:09:00.239 --> 00:09:03.818
I had my back turned to her,
and she started screaming in Farsi.

00:09:04.577 --> 00:09:06.652
The boys fell to the ground laughing.

00:09:06.676 --> 00:09:07.828
I was very confused,

00:09:07.852 --> 00:09:09.926
because there was nothing
funny about this.

00:09:10.390 --> 00:09:12.390
They explained to me that she said,

00:09:12.414 --> 00:09:15.228
"You told me your coach
was a Muslim and a woman."

00:09:15.252 --> 00:09:17.621
From behind, I didn't appear
to be either to her.

00:09:17.645 --> 00:09:21.278
(Laughter)

00:09:21.302 --> 00:09:23.538
"I am Muslim," I said, turning to her.

00:09:23.562 --> 00:09:25.493
"Ašhadu ʾan lā ʾilāha ʾilla (A)llāh,"

00:09:25.517 --> 00:09:27.886
reciting the Muslim declaration of faith.

00:09:28.587 --> 00:09:29.891
Confused,